{"tid":2384900,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"何栢良：污水驗武肺有滯後","createTime":"2021-01-28T18:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T18:40:35.000Z","uid":51754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7cf97ccb31c279a80da996e59734f4b84f8facf","tid":2384900,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"環境局局長黃錦星稱，現時每日最多可在二十多個採樣點用污水檢測，認為技術對抗疫有輔助作用，但承認不一定能找出確診者；港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良也指污水採樣有局限。<br />\n<br />\n黃錦星：「如果是呈陽性的，一定或很大機會是有病毒來源，我們檢測不到，不等於是沒有(確診者)，大家明白這是較粗略的雷達。一個群組與人的生活習慣、他何時去洗手間，或污水那裡有否駁錯渠、渠是否在舊區，如果駁去清水井、不是污水井，這些也會檢測不到。」<br />\n<br />\n何栢良：「不是每一個感染者都在糞便中有病毒，所以在污水裡檢測陽性，<strong><span class=\"red\">首先有時間上滯後，到底滯後多少，現時暫時不掌握</span></strong>，就算污水檢測陰性，不等於那大廈沒個案或傳播鏈。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421996&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=271548e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421996&h=74c65b2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421996</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>證明港共政權搞街區污水鳩驗係冇撚意思<br />\n一個中咗，之後就喺返佢同一街區鳩抽一個水辦去驗，梗係仍然驗返佢啲武肺出嚟<br />\n然後就要全街區所有人攬炒強檢，根本就係為驗而驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"c61a3629468ce3eafeeef2a991a45f689eeeee96","tid":2384900,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:27:31.000Z","msg":"遲下18區求其拎個空氣樣本話有<br />\n<br />\n之後封晒成區拎dna<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8838f344ca8291873a18431ddaac53ea3e72f55c","tid":2384900,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f6124fe27f4f6b90079e30bd230c4dc29f4b1d","tid":2384900,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"滯後就走唔到喺疫情前面㗎喇！"},{"pid":"263e462e29d607473fee987498f5a3ccd9feeb20","tid":2384900,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:39:23.000Z","msg":"而家要封區就係為全民檢測鋪路"},{"pid":"c56c60eb78685434dd0462d1da9507b4fcae75fd","tid":2384900,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f6124fe27f4f6b90079e30bd230c4dc29f4b1d","tid":2384900,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"滯後就走唔到喺疫情前面㗎喇！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:40:35.000Z","msg":"政府一直都俾疫情牽住走架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}